// iPhone-style bumper case â€“ realistic, medium complexity
// Outer dimensions: ~70 mm x 145 mm x 9 mm
// Inner cavity: ~65 mm x 140 mm x 8 mm
// Wall thickness: 2.5 mm everywhere, 100 % printable without support

